      "created_at": "2023-04-20T02:21:10.473Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I am using slope workouts extensively. I think I found a bug. Let\u2019s say I create a workout like this:</p>\n<div class=\"md-table\">\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Minutes</th>\n<th></th>\n<th>FTP%</th>\n<th></th>\n<th>Type</th>\n<th></th>\n<th>Slope%</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>:30</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>50</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>slope</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>:30</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>100</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>slope</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>:30</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>150</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>slope</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>:30</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>50</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>slope</td>\n<td></td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div><p>It will correctly start at 0%, then switch to 1%, then 2% but then instead of going back to 0% it will stay at 2%. If I change the last interval to 1%, then it will correctly work.</p>\n<p>It seems the issue is when you use 0, the app treats it as if no value is provided! I would consider this a bug. Would you agree?</p>\n<p>Thanks,<br>\nD.</p>",
